{"id":32265,"date":"2019-06-18T11:09:31","date_gmt":"2019-06-18T07:09:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=32265"},"modified":"2023-02-27T14:47:42","modified_gmt":"2023-02-27T10:47:42","slug":"which-handle-islam-reliable","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/which-handle-islam-reliable\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Love: Which handle of Islam is most reliable?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: We were sitting with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201c<strong>Which handle of Islam is the most firm?<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cPrayer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>It is good, but that is not it.<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cCharity.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>It is good, but that is not it<\/strong>.\u201d They said, \u201cFasting the month of Ramadan.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>It is good, but that is not it<\/strong>.\u201d They said, \u201cThe Hajj pilgrimage.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>It is good, but that is not it.<\/strong>\u201d They said, \u201cJihad.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>It is good, but that is not it. Verily, the most trustworthy handle of faith is to love and hatred for the sake of Allah.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 18524<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em>Hasan li ghayrihi<\/em> (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0632\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u062c\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064b\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\